did.unittitle: Jennings Wood collection of Confederate imprints
did.abstract: Collection consists of 328 Confederate imprints, most are pamphlet size or smaller. They cover a wide range of topics, but focus mostly on government and public records and laws. All are listed in "Confederate imprints", by M.L. Crandall (E483.C72). This collection is not a complete set.

prefercite.head: Preferred citation
prefercite.p: Jennings Wood collection of Confederate imprints, Special Collections Research Center, The George Washington University.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Jennings Wood, a rare book dealer, donated the collection of Confederate imprints to the library in 1980.

userestrict.head: Restrictions on Use
userestrict.p: Some material may be copyrighted or restricted. It is the patron's obligation to determine and satisfy copyright or other case restrictions when publishing or otherwise distributing materials found in the collections.

bioghist.head: Historical or Biographical Note
bioghist.p: Jennings Wood, a rare book dealer, donated the collection of Confederate imprints to the library in 1980.

scopecontent.head: Collection Scope and Content
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of 328 Confederate imprints, most are pamphlet size or smaller. They cover a wide range of topics, but focus mostly on government and public records and laws. All are listed in "Confederate imprints", by M.L. Crandall (E483.C72). This collection is not a complete set; the Special Collections copy of the Crandall book is annotated to indicate which documents are in this collection. Please note: the original imprint numbers are used as item numbers, therefore the numbers are not in sequential numerical order.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: This collection is open for research.
